Code 
genescolor <- c("#e28743", "#022a5b", "#025b07", "#000306", "#45025b", "#97e87b", "#887be8", "#361cff", "#FFFF1C", "#1cffa7", "#1ccfff", "#881cff", "#80FF1C", "#FF1C20")

ggplot(data = surveys, mapping = aes(x = weight, y = species, color = species) )  + scale_color_manual(values = genescolor) + geom_jitter(color = 'tomato', alpha = 0.2) + geom_boxplot(outlier.shape = NA)

```{r setup}
library('tidyverse')
surveys <- read_csv(here::here('Labs', 'lab2', 'surveys.csv'))
```

```{r}
genescolor <- c("#e28743", "#022a5b", "#025b07", "#000306", "#45025b", "#97e87b", "#887be8", "#361cff", "#FFFF1C", "#1cffa7", "#1ccfff", "#881cff", "#80FF1C", "#FF1C20")

ggplot(data = surveys, mapping = aes(x = weight, y = species, color = species) )  + scale_color_manual(values = genescolor) + geom_jitter(color = 'tomato', alpha = 0.2) + geom_boxplot(outlier.shape = NA)

```
